    <p class="article__paragraph">Unfortunately, many industries still prioritize financial gain over animal welfare. From factory farming and animal testing to deforestation that displaces countless wild creatures, human activities continue to threaten animal populations around the world. By advocating for the protection of animals and choosing cruelty-free alternatives — whether it’s plant-based food like vegan burgers, sustainable clothing, or animal-free cosmetics — consumers can help reduce this unnecessary harm.</p>
